aa(lp124
VAnd on the many times I saw Nathaniel on Skid Row,
p125
aVI witnessed how music was able to bring him back
p126
aVfrom his very darkest moments, from what seemed to me
p127
aVin my untrained eye to be
p128
aVthe beginnings of a schizophrenic episode.
