aVPlaying for Nathaniel, the music took on a deeper meaning,
p130
aVbecause now it was about communication,
p131
aVa communication where words failed, a communication
p132
aVof a message that went deeper than words, that registered
p133
aVat a fundamentally primal level in Nathaniel's psyche,
p134
aVyet came as a true musical offering from me.
